name: Tez Dizpenser ⁄ Saturn ⁄ SYSTEMA SOLARIS ⁄ #4
description: Meet Saturn. SYSTEMA SOLARIS is a series of 10 works that captures the sheer beauty and size of our solar system. Each unique 1 of 1 Tez Dizpenser showcases that celestial body's scale, moon(s), rings, color and its distant view of the sun. Join me on this space-bound voyage. Collect them all! 〔 Diameter: 74,897 mi 〕〔 Length of Day: 10.7 hr 〕〔 Distance from Sun: 891 million mi 〕〔 Average Temperature: -220°F 〕〔 Number of Moons: 82 〕 Twitter: @cmilburndesign – Clubhouse: @codestrong
